    "story_section": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "settings": {
        "text_alignment": "start",
        "content_width": "medium",
        "color_scheme": "standard-primary"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "story-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "We started Codebase because we kept seeing the same problem",
            "size": "3xl"
          }
        },
        "story-body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Businesses would hire an agency, get a pretty mockup, and then discover six months later that the thing could not scale, could not integrate with their existing tools, or could not be maintained without calling the original team.</p><p>We wanted to build differently. Every project starts with understanding the problem, not the pixel. We write clean, documented code that your next developer can pick up without a translator. We choose boring technology when boring technology is the right answer. And we stay involved after launch because products are never finished.</p><p>Codebase is a three-person studio based in Portland. We have been building digital products since 2019. We are small by choice because it means every client gets senior-level attention from discovery through deployment.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["story-heading", "story-body"]
    },
    "approach_section": {
      "type": "image-text",
      "settings": {
        "image_position": "end",
        "text_position": "center",
        "color_scheme": "standard-secondary"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "approach-eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our Approach</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true
          }
        },
        "approach-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Simple code that solves real problems",
            "size": "4xl"
          }
        },
        "approach-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We do not over-engineer. We do not chase frameworks. We pick the right tool for the job, write clear code, ship early, and iterate based on real usage. Every technical decision is made to serve the product, not to impress other developers.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["approach-eyebrow", "approach-heading", "approach-text"]
    },
